OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother hot day, with daytime
OL,6,Ftemperatures widely above average. Dry
OL,7,Fand predominantly clear with hazy
OL,8,Fsunshine in the morning. Cooler along
OL,9,Fcoastal areas, with an onshore breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FGenerally clear skies with
OL,12,Fsome occasional thin high cloud at
OL,13,Ftimes. A northeasterly breeze develops
OL,14,Fbringing low cloud and patchy fog onto
OL,15,Fthe coast and into eastern areas by
OL,16,Fdawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
