OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FEarly morning low cloud
OL,6,Fquickly burning back, turning sunny by
OL,7,Fthe afternoon before low cloud returns
OL,8,Fin a freshening northeasterly wind.
OL,9,FTemperatures very warm but cooler
OL,10,Falong the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FEarly
OL,13,Fmorning low cloud quickly burning
OL,14,Fback, turning sunny by the afternoon
OL,15,Fon Sunday. Dry with plenty of sunshine
OL,16,Fon Monday, thundery showers overnight.
OL,17,FTuesday showers easing but remaining
OL,18,Fcloudy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
